[[File:Bardur chathead.png|left]]
'''Bardur''' can be found deep inside the [[Waterbirth Island Dungeon]], fighting [[dagannoth fledgeling]]s. He will trade the player a [[shark|cooked shark]] in exchange for a [[Fremennik blade]], [[Fremennik shield|shield]], or [[Fremennik helm|helm]], any of which are obtainable as drops from [[dagannoth]]s. 
[[File:Waterbirth_Dungeon_Map.png|thumb|left|Location of Bardur.]]
During [[The Fremennik Exiles]] quest, players can buy a [[Fremennik shield]] from him for 150,000 coins, or [[ring of Charos#Activated|charm]] him into giving it to you for free.

